'''麥肯齊·霍爾頓'''（{{lang-en|Mackenzie Horton}}；{{bd|1996年|4月25日||}}），暱稱'''麥克·霍爾頓'''（{{lang|en|Mack Horton}}），出生於[[澳洲|澳洲]][[墨爾本|墨爾本]]，是一位澳大利亚游泳運動員。他擅長[[自由泳|自由泳]]，曾代表澳大利亞參加了2014年英聯邦運動會、2016年里约奥运会。<ref>{{cite web|title=Results of the boys' 1500 metre freestyle at the 2012 Junior Pan Pacific Swimming Championships|url=http://www.swmeets.com/realtime/jr%20panpacs/2012/120823F008.htm|publisher=Pan Pacific Swimming Association|date=2012-08-24|accessdate=2014-08-20|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304191427/http://www.swmeets.com/realtime/jr%20panpacs/2012/120823F008.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

霍顿曾因数次表达对对手[[孙杨|孙杨]]的不满而备受争议。2016年里约奥运会，他讽刺孙杨是“嗑药的骗子”<ref name="abc20160807">{{cite web|title=Rio 2016: Gold medal winner Mack Horton trolled online after calling out 'drug cheat' Sun Yang|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2016-08-07/rio-2016-mack-horton-trolled-calls-out-sun-yang-drug-cheat/7698746|date=2016-08-06|accessdate=2016-08-06|archive-date=2016-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160808143221/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2016-08-07/rio-2016-mack-horton-trolled-calls-out-sun-yang-drug-cheat/7698746|dead-url=no}}</ref>；2019年游泳世锦赛，他又在颁奖仪式期间拒绝和孙杨合影<ref name=A/>。

== 职业生涯 ==
霍顿于2012年首次代表澳大利亚参赛，比赛是2012年青少年[[泛太平洋游泳錦標賽|泛太平洋游泳锦标赛]]。他在该比赛中以15:10.07的成绩赢得1500米[[自由泳|自由泳]]金牌，还取得了该比赛中400米自由泳第二名和800米自由泳第4名的成绩。

他在两个月后举行的2012年新加坡[[游泳世界杯|游泳世界杯]]中，以14:54.25的成绩取得1500米[[自由泳|自由泳]]冠军。

在2013年[[澳大利亞青年奧運會|澳大利亞青年奧運會]]上，霍顿再次赢得了1500米自由泳项目的金牌<ref>{{cite web|title=Results of the boys' 1500 metre freestyle at the 2013 Australian Youth Olympic Festival|url=http://results.amo-sport.com/(S(nnlgogqcrlptpnpfzr1cctcc))/Results.aspx?EventID=21&SDID=1,14|publisher=[[澳大利亞奧林匹克委員會|澳大利亞奧林匹克委員會]]|date=January 2013|accessdate=2014-08-20}}{{dead link|date=2018年2月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

八个月后，他在于迪拜举行的[[2013年世界青年游泳锦标赛|2013年世界青年游泳锦标赛]]上，获得五枚金牌和一枚银牌。他参加了200米、<ref>{{cite web |title=Results of the boys' 200-metre freestyle final at the 2013 FINA World Junior Swimming Championships |url=http://www.fina.org/H2O/docs/events/swjuniors2013/results.pdf |page=[http://www.fina.org/H2O/docs/events/swjuniors2013/results.pdf#page=42 42] |format=pdf |publisher=[[國際游泳聯合會|國際游泳聯合會]] |date=2013-08-31 |accessdate=2014-08-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728150635/http://www.fina.org/H2O/docs/events/swjuniors2013/results.pdf |archivedate=2014-07-28 }}</ref>400米、<ref>{{cite web |title=Results of the boys' 400-metre freestyle final at the 2013 FINA World Junior Swimming Championships |url=http://www.fina.org/H2O/docs/events/swjuniors2013/results.pdf |page=[http://www.fina.org/H2O/docs/events/swjuniors2013/results.pdf#page=1 1] |format=pdf |publisher=[[國際游泳聯合會|國際游泳聯合會]] |date=2013-08-31 |accessdate=2014-08-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728150635/http://www.fina.org/H2O/docs/events/swjuniors2013/results.pdf |archivedate=2014-07-28 }}</ref>800米<ref>{{cite web |title=Results of the boys' 800-metre freestyle final at the 2013 FINA World Junior Swimming Championships |url=http://www.fina.org/H2O/docs/events/swjuniors2013/results.pdf |page=[http://www.fina.org/H2O/docs/events/swjuniors2013/results.pdf#page=73 73] |format=pdf |publisher=[[國際游泳聯合會|國際游泳聯合會]] |date=2013-08-31 |accessdate=2014-08-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728150635/http://www.fina.org/H2O/docs/events/swjuniors2013/results.pdf |archivedate=2014-07-28 }}</ref>及1500米自由泳的比赛<ref>{{cite web |title=Results of the boys' 1500 metre freestyle final at the 2013 FINA World Junior Swimming Championships |url=http://www.fina.org/H2O/docs/events/swjuniors2013/results.pdf |page=[http://www.fina.org/H2O/docs/events/swjuniors2013/results.pdf#page=141 141] |format=pdf |publisher=[[國際游泳聯合會|國際游泳聯合會]] |date=2013-08-31 |accessdate=2014-08-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728150635/http://www.fina.org/H2O/docs/events/swjuniors2013/results.pdf |archivedate=2014-07-28 }}</ref>，并且与卢克·帕西（{{lang|en|Luke Percy}}）、里根·莱恩（{{lang|en|Regan Leong}}）和布莱克·琼斯（{{lang|en|Blake Jones}}）一同赢得了4×100米自由泳接力赛冠军<ref>{{cite web |title=Results of the boys' 4 × 100-metre freestyle final at the 2013 FINA World Junior Swimming Championships |url=http://www.fina.org/H2O/docs/events/swjuniors2013/results.pdf |page=[http://www.fina.org/H2O/docs/events/swjuniors2013/results.pdf#page=23 23] |format=pdf |publisher=[[國際游泳聯合會|國際游泳聯合會]] |date=2013-08-31 |accessdate=2014-08-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728150635/http://www.fina.org/H2O/docs/events/swjuniors2013/results.pdf |archivedate=2014-07-28 }}</ref>。由霍顿、莱恩、伊萨克·琼斯（{{lang|en|Isaac Jones}}）和杰克·麦卡劳林（{{lang|en|Jack McLoughlin}}）组成的团队在4×200米自由泳接力赛中拿到了第二名，仅次于英国。<ref>{{cite web |title=Results of the boys' 4 × 200-metre freestyle final at the 2013 FINA World Junior Swimming Championships |url=http://www.fina.org/H2O/docs/events/swjuniors2013/results.pdf |page=[http://www.fina.org/H2O/docs/events/swjuniors2013/results.pdf#page=95 95] |format=pdf |publisher=[[國際游泳聯合會|國際游泳聯合會]] |date=2013-08-31 |accessdate=2014-08-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728150635/http://www.fina.org/H2O/docs/events/swjuniors2013/results.pdf |archivedate=2014-07-28 }}</ref>

在2014年[[澳大利亚游泳锦标赛|澳大利亚游泳锦标赛]]上，霍顿首次参加成人比赛，并在1500米自由泳比赛中以14:51.55的成绩取得第一，<ref>{{cite web|title=Results of the men's 1500 metre freestyle final at the 2014 Australian Swimming Championships|url=http://liveresults.swimming.org.au/sal/2014OPEN1/140401F056.htm|publisher={{tsl|en|Swimming Australia}}|date=2014-04-06|accessdate=2014-08-20|archive-date=2015-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151006173236/http://liveresults.swimming.org.au/sal/2014OPEN1/140401F056.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>在400米自由泳项目中以3:44.60的成绩位于小组第二<ref>{{cite web|title=Results of the men's 400-metre freestyle final at the 2014 Australian Swimming Championships|url=http://liveresults.swimming.org.au/sal/2014OPEN1/140401F004.htm|publisher={{tsl|en|Swimming Australia}}|date=2014-04-01|accessdate=2014-08-20|archive-date=2015-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151006183031/http://liveresults.swimming.org.au/sal/2014OPEN1/140401F004.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，打破了两项
{{link-en|青年游泳世界纪录|List of Junior world records in swimming}}<ref>{{cite journal|first=Jason|last=Marsteller|title=FINA world junior records can begin being set today|url=http://www.swimmingworldmagazine.com/news/fina-world-junior-records-can-begin-being-set-today/|journal={{tsl|en|Swimming World Magazine}}|publisher=Sports Publications International|date=2014-04-01|accessdate=2014-08-20|archive-date=2016-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160921115035/http://www.swimmingworldmagazine.com/news/fina-world-junior-records-can-begin-being-set-today/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，他在200米自由泳的比赛中取得1:47.36的成绩<ref>{{cite web|title=Results of the men's 200-metre freestyle final at the 2014 Australian Swimming Championships|url=http://liveresults.swimming.org.au/sal/2014OPEN1/140401F017.htm|publisher={{tsl|en|Swimming Australia}}|date=2014-04-02|accessdate=2014-08-20|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304083538/http://liveresults.swimming.org.au/sal/2014OPEN1/140401F017.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也创造了一项纪录<ref>{{cite journal|first=Jason|last=Marsteller|title=Thomas Fraser-Holmes proves successful with difficult double on night two of Aussie nationals|url=http://www.swimmingworldmagazine.com/news/thomas-fraser-holmes-proves-successful-with-difficult-double-on-night-two-of-aussie-nationals/|journal={{tsl|en|Swimming World Magazine}}|publisher=Sports Publications International|date=2014-04-02|accessdate=2014-08-20|archive-date=2014-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141101092842/http://www.swimmingworldmagazine.com/news/thomas-fraser-holmes-proves-successful-with-difficult-double-on-night-two-of-aussie-nationals/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

