web/20140729135434/http://results.glasgow2014.com/event/swimming/swm014101/mens_400m_freestyle_final.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>在4×200米自由泳接力赛中，霍顿同[[托马斯·弗雷泽-霍尔姆斯|托马斯·弗雷泽-霍尔姆斯]]、[[戴维·麦基翁|戴维·麦基翁]]和[[内德·麦肯德里|内德·麦肯德里]]以1:49.17成为第一名。<ref>{{cite web|title=Results of heat 2 of the men's 4 × 200-metre freestyle relay at the 2014 Commonwealth Games|url=http://results.glasgow2014.com/event/swimming/swm412902/mens_4_x_200m_freestyle_relay___heat_2.html|publisher=Glasgow 2014|date=2014-08-03|accessdate=2014-08-20|archive-date=2014-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140730080054/http://results.glasgow2014.com/event/swimming/swm412902/mens_4_x_200m_freestyle_relay___heat_2.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Results of the men's 4 × 200-metre freestyle relay final at the 2014 Commonwealth Games|url=http://results.glasgow2014.com/event/swimming/swm412101/mens_4_x_200m_freestyle_relay_final.html|publisher=Glasgow 2014|date=2014-08-03|accessdate=2014-08-20|archive-date=2014-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140810211044/http://results.glasgow2014.com/event/swimming/swm412101/mens_4_x_200m_freestyle_relay_final.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

